column1: Regular traffic reports will resume Wednesday December 12 at 4:00 p.m.

column3: US-27 at N Main St in Jessamine Co:
column4: Overturned tanker truck with gasoline and diesel spill.  All lanes in both directions are shutdown until further notice.

column3: US-27 at N Main St in Jessamine Co:
